OL,3,CFuneral held for British aid worker
OL,4,CJames Kirby who was killed in Gaza
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FHundreds gathered for the funeral of
OL,8,Faid worker James Kirby who was killed
OL,9,Fin an Israeli air strike in Gaza.
OL,11,FMr Kirby, 47, was working for the aid
OL,12,Fgroup World Central Kitchen when his
OL,13,Fconvoy was struck on 1 April.
OL,15,FSeven people were killed in the
OL,16,Fattack, including fellow British aid
OL,17,Fworkers John Chapman, 57, and James
OL,18,F"Jim" Henderson, 33.
