OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FAlso killed were the relief team's
OL,8,Fleader, Australian national Lalzawmi
OL,9,F"Zomi" Frankcom, dual American-
OL,10,FCanadian citizen Jacob Flickinger,
OL,11,FPolish national Damian Sobol and their
OL,12,Fdriver, Palestinian Saifeddin Issam
OL,13,FAyad Abutaha.
OL,15,FMr Kirby's funeral was held at St Mary
OL,16,FRedcliffe Church in Bristol on
OL,17,FWednesday 15 May.
OL,19,FAhead of the funeral, and described
OL,20,Fhim as a "remarkable man" and a "true
OL,21,Ffriend to many".
