OL,7,F"I cannot express more deeply my
OL,8,Fgratitude for the outpouring of love I
OL,9,Fhave seen over the weeks since his
OL,10,Ftragic death in Gaza," she said.
OL,12,F"I will miss him beyond measure and
OL,13,Fcannot comprehend a future without his
OL,14,Fpresence."
OL,16,FSeveral family members and friends
OL,17,Fspoke at the funeral, sharing stories
OL,18,Fand memories with Mr Kirby.
