OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FHis cousin, Adam, said "Thank you for
OL,8,Fyour boundless love, your unwavering
OL,9,Fselflessness and the countless
OL,10,Fmemories you've left imprinted on our
OL,11,Fhearts.
OL,13,F"You will forever be loved, deeply
OL,14,Fmissed, forever remembered by all of
OL,15,Fthose you touched."
OL,17,FReflecting on memories with Mr Kirby,
OL,18,Fanother cousin, Andre, described how
OL,19,FJames would always make time to visit
OL,20,Fhim and his family at their home.
