OL,7,FHe described him as a "constant,
OL,8,Fcalming presence".
OL,10,FHe said: "He was always willing to
OL,11,Fhelp, that was Kirbs. Always offering
OL,12,Fto help others until the end."
OL,14,F"The one thing we always think we have
OL,15,Fis time," he added. "Time to make the
OL,16,Fphone call, time with family and
OL,17,Ffriends and time to make those
OL,18,Fmemories but things can change in the
OL,19,Fblink of an eye which is why I think
OL,20,FKirbs crammed so much fun and
OL,21,Fadventure into his life.
