OL,7,FOne of Mr Kirby's childhood friends,
OL,8,FBrendon Forbes, spoke to ITV News
OL,9,Fafter the funeral. he recalled how
OL,10,Fthey met as army cadets in Weston-
OL,11,Fsuper-Mare at 13 year's old and formed
OL,12,Fa lifelong bond.
OL,14,FDescribing him, he said "He was
OL,15,Fgentle, he was always funny, he was
OL,16,Falways considerate."
OL,18,FViener Gaston met Mr Kirby in 2010
OL,19,Fwhen they were stationed together in
OL,20,FAfghanistan.
