OL,7,F"He was my cover man and I was his
OL,8,Fpoint man," he said.
OL,10,FHe recalled how Mr Kirby would always
OL,11,Fremain calm in every situation.
OL,13,F"It didn't matter if you were upset,
OL,14,Fif you were afraid of something, he
OL,15,Fwould make you feel better. He would
OL,16,Fmake you feel good about yourself.
OL,18,F"He was that driving force behind you.
OL,19,FHe would always say 'don't worry, I'm
OL,20,Falways here to protect you'.
